dct_title_s: La nova descrittione di tutta la patria del Friuli dilignetissimamente esposta
dct_description_sm: per M. Pyrrho Ligorio Napolitano... ; Sebastiano di re da Chiogga intagliava in rame.
Includes ornate title cartouche with pans with pipes, human head, goat head at upper right.
Picture of Lion of St Mark suspended from left top corner.
Includes depictions of ships, mountains, forests, routes; explanatory notes regarding geographic features, rivers, watermark.
